BrickBeads #1 Collection
/ .01 The Mac

▪ The first edition of the first collection by this creator. This is a BrickBeads that has started a movement, inspired the vast world of technology and intialised an era which led to the creation of this item you are seeing right now.

▴Features
|
▸London, UK [Location]
▸15:20 / 1:20 PM [Render's Time]
▸13th July 2021 [Render's Day]

• More about the creator: 
- I am a 15Y old digital creator based in London, originally from Italy. 
- I experimented in many fields of design, from logo to 3D to poster to even architecture... essentially loving the space.
- I am finding ways to express my art throught the world of digital NFTs, finding my way now onto Foundation to gain more support and attention.
